  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0002",
      "text": " 71",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.24",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        123.74,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0004",
      "text": "Registered Link Incident Report (RLIR)",
      "bbox": [
        133.8,
        57.65,
        317.73,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0005",
      "text": "4.2.24.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        192.63,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0006",
      "text": "The following terms are used to reference the ports, nodes, and records related to link incident re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        540.07,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0007",
      "text": "porting:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        129.3,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0008",
      "text": "a) incident port: The port on which the link incident occurred and that detected the link incident.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        142.96,
        529.66,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0009",
      "text": "b) connected port or connected node: The port or node connected directly to the incident port by a",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        166.96,
        540.03,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0010",
      "text": "Fibre Channel link.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        178.96,
        205.67,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0011",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        202.96,
        114.38,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0012",
      "text": "reporting port: The port that sends the Link Incident Record.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        202.96,
        386.83,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0013",
      "text": "d) registered port: A port that is registered with the reporting port to receive link incident reports.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        226.96,
        532.86,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0014",
      "text": "e) reporting node: The node that creates the Link Incident Record describing the incident on the",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        250.96,
        540.01,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0015",
      "text": "incident port.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        262.96,
        179.55,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0016",
      "text": "The RLIR ELS shall provide a method for a reporting Nx_Port to send a Link Incident Record to a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        539.89,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0017",
      "text": "registered Nx_Port.  The normal response to an RLIR ELS Sequence shall be a LS_ACC ELS Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.08,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0018",
      "text": "quence with no Payload.  If the recipient Nx_Port does not support the RLIR ELS, it shall reply with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        539.87,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0019",
      "text": "an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason code of \"Command not supported\".  If the recipient Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        540.01,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0020",
      "text": "is unable to accept the specified Link Incident Record type, it shall reply with an LS_RJT ELS Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.95,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0021",
      "text": "quence with a reason code of \"Unable to perform command request\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        401.98,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0022",
      "text": "A port shall recognize a link incident when a condition is detected for which an incident code (see ta-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        539.97,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0023",
      "text": "ble 72) is defined.  When a link incident is recognized and a recipient of Link Incident Records is reg-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.96,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0024",
      "text": "istered for the incident port, a Link Incident Record that contains information related to the link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        539.99,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0025",
      "text": "incident shall be created.  When a Link Incident Record is generated, the reporting port shall use the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        540.0,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0026",
      "text": "link incident reporting procedure to pass the Link Incident Record to a registered port.  The link inci-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        540.07,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0027",
      "text": "dent reporting mechanism, if any, for a port that does not use this link incident reporting procedure is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        540.03,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0028",
      "text": "beyond the scope of this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        248.77,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0029",
      "text": "After a Link Failure is detected, the reporting node may delay recognizing and considering this link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        539.99,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0030",
      "text": "failure as a reportable link incident condition, for a specific period of time.  Some FC-4 protocols may",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        539.97,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0031",
      "text": "be capable of transparently recovering from a Link Failure condition, and may not generate a Link In-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.04,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0032",
      "text": "cident Record.  If the Link Failure condition persists for longer than the FC-4 specified time out peri-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.08,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0033",
      "text": "od, then a Link Incident Record is generated and reported.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        354.37,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0034",
      "text": "4.2.24.2  Link Incident reporting procedure",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        297.64,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0035",
      "text": "The incident port's reporting node shall generate one Link Incident Record for each link incident.  The",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        540.01,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0036",
      "text": "number of Link Incident Records a reporting node may hold is vendor specific.  If the incident port’s",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        540.0,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0037",
      "text": "reporting node attempts to generate a Link Incident Record but does not have resources to hold the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.03,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0038",
      "text": "record, the oldest Link Incident Record shall be discarded, and the new Link Incident Record shall be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        539.99,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0039",
      "text": "retained.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        134.89,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0040",
      "text": "The port selected as the reporting port by the reporting node shall present the Link Incident Records",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        540.06,
        646.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0041",
      "text": "by sending RLIR ELSs to ports registered as valid recipients of Link Incident Records.  After sending",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        539.97,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0042",
      "text": "all required RLIR ELSs containing the Link Incident Record, the port may discard the Link Incident",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        539.95,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p090_s0043",
      "text": "Record.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        130.98,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}